Titolo: Midtown Madness 3

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Midtown Madness 3 is a 2003 open world racing video game developed by Digital Illusions CE on the Xbox. It is the third game in the Midtown Madness series.
The game was developed by Digital Illusions CE and published by Microsoft Game Studios. This marked a change from the developer of the first two games, Angel Studios, which had moved on to work on the Midnight Club series. The Xbox-only release and change of developer heralded a significant graphical improvement to maintain the console's graphical standards.